                <li>Predict and prevent equipment failures</li>
                <li>Optimize chemical dosing and energy consumption</li>
                <li>Achieve higher treatment efficiency and compliance</li>
                <li>Adapt to changing influent characteristics</li>
              </ul>
          
              <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                Support sustainable operations with lower costs and environmental impact. 
                This is not just automation, but intelligence in action — turning raw environmental data into actionable insights 
                that drive better decisions, improve plant performance, and ensure long-term sustainability for our clients.
              </p>
              
